This is my personal Gentoo overlay. Used for personal projects and followed projects.

Adding overlay with 'layman' :
     $ layman -f -a linkdd-portage -o https://github.com/linkdd/linkdd-overlay/raw/master/overlays.xml

Adding overlay with 'PORTDIR_OVERLAY'
     $ git clone git://github.com/linkdd/linkdd-overlay.git /usr/local/portage
     $ echo "PORTDIR_OVERLAY=\"/usr/local/portage\"" >> /etc/make.conf

Contact me: David Delassus <david.jose.delassus@gmail.com>
